context_text:
[Image @00:01:06.080]: Nguoi cha chi tay vao nhanh cay va giai thich, cau be lang nghe cham chu.
[Dialogue]: Neu chi biet bam vao ben ngoai, den luc than cay yeu thi no cung heo tan.
